  <num>42-3212</num>
  <heading>Consolidation of actions for arrears of rent and possession.</heading>
  <text>If actions be brought separately for arrears of rent and for the possession, they may be afterwards consolidated and 1 judgment rendered in them for the possession and also for the rent.</text>
